---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
    title="About — Alina"
    description="Alina — Growth & Social Media Specialist at Piwi.AI. Helping small businesses grow their online presence with smart content strategies and AI-powered tools."
    canonicalUrl="https://aniteialina.com/about"
>
    <div class="about-page">
        <h1>About Me</h1>

        <div class="about-profile">
            <img src="/profile.png" alt="Alina" class="profile-picture" />
        </div>

        <section class="about-intro">
            <p>
                Hi, I'm <strong>Alina</strong> — a Growth Marketer at
                <a href="https://piwi.ai" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Piwi.AI</a>,
                where we're building AI-powered tools that help businesses work smarter
                with their documents and data.
            </p>
            <p>
                I'm passionate about the intersection of <strong>technology and storytelling</strong>.
                I believe that great marketing isn't about shouting the loudest — it's about
                understanding your audience, creating genuine value, and building connections
                that last.
            </p>
            <p>
                Before joining Piwi.AI, I built my skills across content creation, brand strategy,
                and social media management for businesses of all sizes. I've seen firsthand
                how the right content strategy can transform a small business's visibility
                and growth.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-skills">
            <h2>What I'm Into</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>AI in Marketing</strong> — Exploring how AI tools can make
                    marketers more creative and efficient, not replace them
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Content Strategy</strong> — Building frameworks that help
                    busy business owners create content consistently
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Social Media</strong> — Platform strategy, community building,
                    and authentic engagement
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Brand Storytelling</strong> — Crafting narratives that connect
                    with real people and drive real results
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Small Business Growth</strong> — Practical, no-fluff advice
                    for businesses without a marketing department
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="about-contact">
            <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                I love hearing from fellow marketers, small business owners, and anyone
                curious about AI in marketing. Don't be a stranger!
            </p>
            <div class="contact-links">
                <a
                    href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alina-anitei/"
                    class="btn btn-primary"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noreferrer"
                >
                    LinkedIn
                </a>
                <a
                    href="https://github.com/AniteiAlina"
                    class="btn btn-outline"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noreferrer"
                >
                    GitHub
                </a>
                <a
                    href="https://piwi.ai"
                    class="btn btn-outline"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noreferrer"
                >
                    Piwi.AI
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
